citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:30 p.m. on
13-Aug-20.
In addition to waiting 30 minutes and honking the vehicle horn, I called the phone numbers provided and left a
message.
